Rendell E. de Kort {#title}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Development Economist 

I'm a Development Economist with experience in public policy and macro economic analysis and forecasting. In normal times I focus on assisting social enterprises with economic/ financial advisory services and aiding organizations leverage data analytics. Since COVID-19 I have been actively contributing to the discussions on the macro-economy through informative content aimed at the general public and through participation in the National commission to design a new economic future for Aruba, chaired by the prime minister. 



